		<title>CC BY-SA 4.0 now one-way compatible with GPLv3 - remark</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://text.baldanders.info/remark/2015/cc-by-sa-4-now-one-way-compatible-with-gplv3/" />
